CustomField.description: Date of Birth in YYYY-MM-DD format. Use to calculate age for eligibility determination. Capture during phone enrollment. Format examples: 1980-05-15, 1995-12-25.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Enter the candidate's date of birth in YYYY-MM-DD format (e.g., 1980-05-15). This is used to calculate age for eligibility determination.
